        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Phase 4: Verifying Reduction and Retiring Items"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "After deploying an automation, verify that it actually reduced toil. Check the on-call log for the next two weeks. If the toil event count drops to zero, retire the item from the toil backlog. If it persists, the automation has a bug or an edge case."
          }
        ]
      },
